views.text: Japanese Prime Minister Shinzo Abe announces his intention to resign due to medical concerns.
Hurricane Laura kills at least 36 people across the Caribbean and the United States.
The Africa Regional Certification Commission declares that wild polio has been eliminated in Africa.
Italian businessman Libero Grassi was killed by the Sicilian Mafia after taking a public stand against their extortion demands.
Organized crime syndicate originating in Sicily
